        <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold text-blue-600 mb-6">CloudKeep Privacy Policy</h1>
        <p class="text-gray-500 text-sm mb-6">Effective Date: <span class="font-semibold">[March 8, 2025]</span></p>

        <p class="mb-6">
            CloudKeep is committed to protecting your privacy. This Privacy Policy outlines how we collect, use, store, and share your personal information when you use our cloud storage services, which include a free plan (up to 5 GB of storage) and two paid plans (15 GB and 25 GB, respectively).
        </p>

        <!-- Section 1 -->
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-4">1. Acceptance of This Policy</h2>
        <p class="mb-6">
            By accessing or using CloudKeep services, you acknowledge that you have read, understood, and agree to be bound by this Privacy Policy. If you do not agree with our policies and practices, please do not use our services.
        </p>

        <!-- Section 2 -->
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-4">2. Information We Collect</h2>

        <h3 class="text-xl font-medium text-gray-700 mb-2">a. Personal Information</h3>
        <p class="mb-4">
            When you register for CloudKeep, we may ask for personal details including, but not limited to:
        </p>
        <ul class="list-disc list-inside mb-6">
            <li>Name</li>
            <li>Email address</li>
            <li>Contact information</li>
        </ul>
        <p class="mb-6">
            For paid subscription plans, additional billing details (such as credit card information) are processed securely through our payment processor. We do not store full payment details on our servers.
        </p>

        <h3 class="text-xl font-medium text-gray-700 mb-2">b. Usage Information</h3>
        <p class="mb-4">
            We collect information related to your usage of CloudKeep:
        </p>
        <ul class="list-disc list-inside mb-6">
            <li>Files uploaded and storage usage (e.g., free up to 5 GB, 15 GB, or 25 GB in your selected plan)</li>
            <li>Access and activity logs</li>
            <li>Device and browser details</li>
        </ul>

        <h3 class="text-xl font-medium text-gray-700 mb-2">c. Cookies and Tracking Technologies</h3>
        <p class="mb-6">
            We use cookies and similar tracking technologies to enhance user experience, analyze usage trends, and improve our service. You can modify your browser settings to manage cookies; however, this may affect your experience with our site.
        </p>

        <!-- Continue Other Sections Similarly -->
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-4">3. How We Use Your Information</h2>
